  : Parenl Posedge identifier Parenr  { Ltl.posedge (fst $3) }
  | Parenl Negedge identifier Parenr  { Ltl.negedge (fst $3) } 
  | Rose   Parenl  identifier Parenr  { Ltl.posedge (fst $3) }
  | Fell   Parenl  identifier Parenr  { Ltl.negedge (fst $3) }
  ;

